Cummings III (amụrụ na 1938: 61 ) bụ ónyé na-ese ihe na prọfesọ nke nka fine arts na Mahadum California State, Fullerton. Cummings na-eji ihe ndị dị oké ọnụ ahịa eme arịa osisi na oche, nke sitere n'ihe ime mmụọ nke ihe ndị dị n'Africa.
A mụrụ Cummings na Los Angeles, California na 1938

Ọ natara Master of Arts ya na Mahadum California State, Fullerton na 1971. N'afọ 1973, Cummings natara ònyínyé site na National Endowment for the Arts iji nọrọ ọnwa abụọ na Ghana na-enyocha myirịta dị n'etiti ọgụ njirimara nke ndị Africa America na ọgụ ndị ha chere ihu n'Africa. N'afọ 1981, ọ laghachiri Africa, gosipụta ọrụ ya na Gabon, Ghana, Madagascar, na Malawi.
Ihe ngosi nka mbụ nkè Cummings, Sensitivity, dị na Long Beach Museum of Art na 1974.: 109 A ka na-egosi ọrụ ya na ebe ngosi nka.

Nchịkọta Lipton nwèrè arịa osisi nke Cummings mere. Museum of Fine Arts, Boston, Minneapolis Institute of Art, na Smithsonian American Art Museum nwèrè ihe Cummings na nchịkọta ha. E gosipụtara ọrụ ya na White House Collection of American Craft
